### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "you@example.com",
  "password": "secret12"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "you@example.com",
  "password": "secret12"
}

### Google (ID token from client OAuth)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Username available?
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/usernames/clever_panda_42/available

### Me (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Patch profile
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/me/avatar/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/v1/me/status/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/v1/media/chat/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "chat_s1",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/v1/media/read-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mediaKey": "chat/ACCOUNT-UUID/chat_s1/FILE-UUID.jpg"
}

###

PATCH http://localhost:8080/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rahul",
  "username": "clever_panda_42",
  "dob": "2000-05-15",
  "gender": "M",
  "profileComplete": true
}

### Delete account
DELETE http://localhost:8080/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
